data.description:
Desirable End Unit!!
This end unit is an excellent opportunity for a hassle-free move that boasts an open living room with a large bay window. Walk into a workable kitchen next to the dining area. This flows into a main floor laundry and half bath. Upstairs you will find a spacious primary bedroom with a full bath. Along with a second bedroom with a large closet. A one-car garage and a low maintenance unit that is furtherest from the street. SELLER IS OFFERING $5000.00 IN SELLER CONFESSIONS Discover the perfect blend of affordability, convenience, and comfort. Schedule a Showing today!
